{"tid":441122,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"首隻電競概念股雷蛇 傳11月上市籌最多47億","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T14:14:31.000Z","uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f7e9c48e00291f8510d4f87428ab51822e2ca5","tid":441122,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"市場消息指，星洲電競設備供應商雷蛇（Razer）已於本周一（16日）通過上市聆訊，現正進行上市前路演，集資額達5億至6億美元（約39至46.8億港元），估計於11月初上市。換言之，兩大互聯網概念股雷蛇及自騰訊（0700）分拆出來的閱文，因為招股時間接近，散戶可能只能「二揀一」，或需攤分注碼抽股。<br />\n<br />\n雷蛇是本港首隻電競概念股，市場消息透露，雷蛇將於11月1日起招股，11月中旬掛牌，瑞信及瑞銀為聯席保薦人。<br />\n<br />\n雷蛇自2005年成立，本港首富李嘉誠旗下維港投資公司Redmount Ventures持有1.29%股權，其他主要投資者還包括英特爾及淡馬錫控股旗下的海麗凱資本等，股東可謂粒粒巨星。據券商的報告預計，雷蛇的估值45億至60億美元（約351億至468億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國上市的易車控股旗下汽車金融子公司易鑫集團，將於今日進行上市聆訊，市傳其融資不超過8億美元（約62億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n至於中港Lego零售商凱知樂亦傳於今日聆訊。凱知樂與多個國際玩具品牌合作，包括樂高、Silverlit、Schleich、Siku、Sieper、Chicco及Aprica等多個著名嬰兒用品品牌，去年8月在旺角朗豪坊開始了第一家LEGO Store，另一間LEGO Certified Store亦已於銅鑼灣時代廣場開幕。<br />\n<br />\n截至2016年底，凱知樂在中國擁有216間零售店，一間香港分店、另設網上商店等。該公司主席、行政總裁為李澄曜，盧永仁為公司執董、副主席、財務總監等。<br />\n<br />\n10月至今，共有11隻新股在港交所上市，除了致浩達（1707）首日每手3,000股蝕120元，其餘全升，賺錢新股中，首日賺錢王是高萌（8065）每手5,000股帳面賺1,450元，首日賺錢能力最低為春能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2515045-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%BB%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%82%A1%E9%9B%B7%E8%9B%87-%E5%82%B311%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E7%B1%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A47%E5%84%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2515045-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%25BB%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E6%25A6%2582%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E8%2582%25A1%25E9%259B%25B7%25E8%259B%2587-%25E5%2582%25B311%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%25B1%258C%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%259A47%25E5%2584%2584&d=SFdoF744aWed7kNU3WVg7ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=eec44f84\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/2515045-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%BB%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E8%82%A1%E9%9B%B7%E8%9B%87-%E5%82%B311%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E7%B1%8C%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A47%E5%84%84</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n名位股神連登仔點睇?"},{"pid":"1b0bd7529e35073a515c6a01316aec030500774d","tid":441122,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:09:30.000Z","msg":"抽"},{"pid":"6be008e93b1cd801051098e35953abbe3d62e59e","tid":441122,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"一定要抽誠哥都有份"},{"pid":"b8f2d53c433d5c19d93d8a43236fd478f0be54db","tid":441122,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要抽誠哥都有份</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠哥漁翁撒網點同你成幅身家掉落去個風險比"},{"pid":"c4722d02279a165609bb7379e98b32aa59b69ee7","tid":441122,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:31:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定要抽誠哥都有份</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 誠哥漁翁撒網點同你成幅身家掉落去個風險比</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點訓身呀, 抽到一手都還神啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd92e27003501cdac77f1600f5d18f5cac70b21","tid":441122,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"呢隻好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd76195694927b5957b3cd208163148fb3820244","tid":441122,"uid":59518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:33:14.000Z","msg":"雷蛇食叉燒"},{"pid":"3ba552e2158f99943cf53189e00a8912f7c2a12d","tid":441122,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13